---

## Standardized API Response Formats

**Successful Response:**
```json
{
  "status": "completed",
  "output": {
    "artifacts": [
      { "type": "text", "text": "response content here" }
    ]
  }
}
```

**Error Response:**
```json
{
  "error": "Error description here",
  "status": "failed",
  "code": "ERROR_CODE"
}
```

